@ECHAddress = http://localhost:5202


///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

### Update product
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chicken Shawarma - Updated",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": 30.0,
  "stockQuantity": 25
}

###! ################################################## !###
###?    ...this is the 1st question in the project...   ?###
###! ################################################## !###
### update quantity unsafely with Race Condition
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/products/decrease-quantity-unsafe/1/3

### update quantity with lock and transaction to avoid race condition 
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/products/decrease-quantity-safe/1/2

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

###! ################################################## !###
###?    ...this is the 2sd question in the project...   ?###
###! ################################################## !###
### decrease quantity with multiple threads with semaphore
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/products/decrease-quantity-controlled/1/2


///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////


### Get cart items (userId = 2)
GET {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart

### Add item to cart
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart/add?productId=2&quantity=11

### Update quantity
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart/update?productId=3&quantity=5

###! ################################################## !###
###?    ...this is the 3ed question in the project...   ?###
###! ################################################## !###
### Create order from cart items sync
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/orders/create-sync

### Create order from cart items async
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/orders/create-async


///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

