###?    ...this is the 4th question in the project...   ?###
###! ################################################## !###
### Generate daily sales report (sync)
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/reports/daily-report-sync

### Generate daily sales report (batch)
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/reports/daily-report-batch


### Generate daily sales report (batch with multiple threads)
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/reports/daily-report-batch-mthreads